## Phase 2: Privacy & Collaboration (Q2-Q3 2026)

**Goal:** Add E2EE and basic collaboration while maintaining privacy-first values

**Duration:** 16-24 weeks (April-September 2026)  
**Effort:** 240-360 hours

### Q2 2026 (April-June):

#### End-to-End Encryption (P0) 🟢 **FREE**
- ✅ 🟢 AES-256-GCM encryption (WebCrypto API) - **FREE (Privacy feature)**
- ✅ 🟢 User-controlled passphrase - **FREE**
- ✅ 🟢 Encrypt before cloud sync - **FREE**
- ✅ 🟢 Key derivation (PBKDF2, 100K iterations) - **FREE**
- ✅ 🟢 Migration tool (encrypt existing plain-text data) - **FREE**

#### Basic Sharing (P1) 🟢 **FREE**
- ✅ 🟢 Share notes (read-only public link) - **FREE**
- ✅ 🔵 Share projects (invite collaborators) - **PRO** (requires collab infrastructure)
- ✅ 🟢 Password-protected shares - **FREE**
- ✅ 🟢 Expiring links (24hr, 7 days, 30 days) - **FREE**

#### Linking & Organization (P1)
- ✅ 🟢 [[Wiki-style links]] between notes - **FREE**
- ✅ 🟢 Backlinks panel (show notes linking here) - **FREE**
- ✅ 🟢 #Tags - **FREE**
- ✅ 🟢 Tag browser/filter - **FREE**
- ✅ 🟢 Inline images (drag-and-drop) - **FREE**

### Q3 2026 (July-September):

#### Real-Time Collaboration (P1) 🔵 **PRO**
- ✅ 🔵 Real-time editing (CRDT library: Yjs or Automerge) - **PRO** (2-5 users) / **ENTERPRISE** (unlimited)
- ✅ 🔵 Presence indicators (who's viewing) - **PRO**
- ✅ 🔵 Cursor tracking (optional, privacy toggle) - **PRO**
- ✅ 🔵 Conflict resolution (automatic merge) - **PRO**

#### Permissions (P2) 🔵 **PRO** / 🟣 **ENTERPRISE**
- ✅ 🔵 Role-based access (Owner, Editor, Viewer) - **PRO** (basic) / **ENTERPRISE** (custom roles)
- ✅ 🔵 Per-note permissions - **PRO**
- ✅ 🔵 Per-project permissions - **PRO**
- ✅ 🟣 Invite system (email or link) - **PRO** (basic) / **ENTERPRISE** (SSO integration)

#### Comments (P2) 🔵 **PRO**
- ✅ 🔵 Comments on notes - **PRO**
- ✅ 🔵 Comments on tasks - **PRO**
- ✅ 🔵 Threaded discussions - **PRO**
- ✅ 🔵 @mentions - **PRO**

### Success Metrics Q2-Q3:
